               <msContents class="lemmatic">
                  <summary>This manuscript contains commentary on the book of Aphorisms attributed to <persName type="standard" ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/287984736" key="person_287984736">Hippocrates</persName>. <title type="main">شرح فصول أبقراط</title> The manuscript contains the following works: 1) Introduction of Abd Latif Baghdadi's commentary on the Aphorisims in <locus n="1-2, 247">ff. 1-2, 247</locus>; 2) a part of Ibn Abi Ṣadiq's commentary on the Aphorisms in <locus n="3-31">ff. 3-31</locus>; 3) Hunayn's Question on Medicine with Ibn Abi Ṣadiq's commentary in <locus n="31-246">ff. 31-246</locus>.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="MS_Or_quart_881-item1">
                     <title xml:lang="ar" key="work_7757">شرح فصول أبقراط</title>
                     <title xml:lang="en" type="desc" key="work_7757">Commentary on Hippocratic Aphorisms</title>
                     <title xml:lang="en" type="alt" key="work_7757">Sharḥ Fusūl Abuqrāṭ</title>
                     <author key="person_81975562">
                        <persName ref="viaf.org/viaf/81975562" type="aut">'Abd al-Lātīf al-Baghdādī‏عبد اللطيف البغدادي</persName>
                     </author>
                     <respStmt>
                        <persName type="supplied" subtype="edt" key="person_81975562">'Abd al-Lātīf al-Baghdādīعبد اللطيف البغدادي</persName>
                        <resp><!--Required resp added in conversion -JC --></resp>
                     </respStmt>
                     <note>Original manuscript in Berlin State Library.</note>
                     <note>The copy is unnamed and undated.</note>
                     <textLang mainLang="ar">Arabic</textLang>
